<doc id="766607" wikidata="Q7738976" url="?curid=766607" title="The Harvill Book of Twentieth-Century Poetry in English">
<text>The Harvill Book of Twentieth-Century Poetry in English is a poetry anthology edited by Michael Schmidt, and published in 1999. Schmidt is an American academic and long-term UK resident, who is the founder of Carcanet Press; he has also written extensive biographical books about poets.

A paperback edition was issued in London by Harvill Press in 2000 with .

